pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Olive Leaf 50ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Olive Leaf is a source of antioxidants to help reduce free radical damage.

Wanderlust Olive Leaf is a consciously created plant-active in a convenient, readily absorbed liquid herbal extract. Olive Leaf is a source of antioxidants to help reduce free radicals formed in the body

Size: 50 mL

Ingredients

EACH 1.25 mL CONTAINS:
Olea europaea (Olive Leaf) leaf ext. liquid 1.13 mL
Derived from dry -----1.13 g

Also contains glycerol and peppermint oil.
Contains 40.5% alcohol.

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours.
Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

You can expect a bitter taste which is typical of herbal extracts and all of their goodness.

Complemented with natural peppermint oil.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Using the measured dropper take 1.25 mL daily, or as directed by your healthcare practitioner. Drop directly onto the tongue or dilute in 30 mL of water or juice and consume immediately. Follow with a glass of water if necessary.

Shake well before use.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat and sunlight. Do not use if cap seal is missing or broken.
